  <section id="intro">
    <title>Introduction and Overview</title>

    <para>The <productname>Mindquarry Document Management
    System</productname>, short <productname>MDMS</productname> is an Open
    Source<footnote>
        <para>Under the conditions of the Mozilla Public License
        (<abbrev>MPL</abbrev>), Version 1.1</para>
      </footnote> version control and document management system that provides
    version controlled access to shared documents, offline synchronization
    with your desktop computer and atom changes.</para>

    <section>
      <title>Design Goals</title>

      <para>The Mindquarry Document Management System will take existing
      Version Control Systems like Subversion, which is the most important
      open source version control system today a step ahead in order to make
      them more accessible for non-technical users.</para>
    </section>
